sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as llama-stack-k8s-operator<br/>Reconciler
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process)
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant ODHBundle as odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap
    participant UserCM as User ConfigMaps

    Note over Admin,UserCM: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    Admin->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (CR change)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Get CR spec & status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

    Note over Operator,Kustomize: Manifest Rendering
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render base manifests
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: 1. Name Prefixer
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: 2. Namespace Setter
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: 3. Field Mutator (ports, replicas, storage)
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: 4. NetworkPolicy Transformer
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources

    Note over Operator,UserCM: CA Bundle Aggregation
    Operator->>ODHBundle: directGet odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    ODHBundle-->>Operator: Platform CA certificates
    Operator->>UserCM: directGet user CA bundle<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    UserCM-->>Operator: User CA certificates
    Operator->>Operator: Validate PEM/X.509 certs<br/>(max 10MB, 1000 certs)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {instance}-ca-bundle ConfigMap

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Resource Application (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Deployment, Service, SA,<br/>PVC, NP, PDB, HPA, RoleBinding
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources applied

    Note over Operator,LlamaStack: Status Probing
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: Version info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

    Note over Admin,LlamaStack: Flow 2: External Client Access (exposeRoute=true)

    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    Client->>Ingress: HTTP request<br/>80/TCP
    Ingress->>LlamaStack: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LlamaStack-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: Response
